<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yé sū ài wǒ 迦南950</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū ài wǒ, yé sū ài wǒ. wǒ zuì qīng chǔ, wǒ zuì xiǎo dé.
 yāng yāng shì jiè tā zhǎo dào wǒ, wān wān zhǎng lù tā péi bàn wǒ.
 wēn yì zāi nán tā kàn gù wǒ. wù huì gōng jī tā ān wèi wǒ.
 yé sū ài wǒ hé děng ài wǒ, wǒ yào gē chàng wǒ yào shù shuō.
 zhè jiāng shì yī gè zuì gǎn rén de gù shì, zhè jiāng shì yī shǒu zuì dòng tīng de shī gē.
 tiān kōng de xiǎo niǎo hé wǒ yī tóng gē chàng, yé sū ài wǒ yǒng yuǎn ài wǒ.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>950</hymn_number>
</song>